    "body": "In this case size==0, and gpr_malloc is returning NULL. There's a documentation bug on gpr_malloc currently (I believe @nicolasnoble should take a look).\n\nCurrently, if size is non-0, gpr_malloc will internally assert if NULL is going to be returned, and if size is 0, it will always return NULL. \n"
